00:25:40,580 --> 00:25:45,250
Now we're at the climax of the show.

386
00:25:45,250 --> 00:25:49,060
Princess Jasmine finally found the most amazing jasmine flowers.

387
00:25:49,060 --> 00:25:52,820
But she decides to use the jasmine flowers to revive her dead lover

388
00:25:52,820 --> 00:25:54,670
