389
00:25:54,670 --> 00:25:57,110
Director, I have some questions.

390
00:25:57,110 --> 00:25:59,030
Ask away.

391
00:25:59,030 --> 00:26:04,100
I don't know which one of them is the lead actor.

392
00:26:05,860 --> 00:26:08,970
<i>[Dream Sets Sail]</i>

393
00:26:08,970 --> 00:26:11,140
Let me think.

394
00:26:14,270 --> 00:26:16,920
Sit down, all of you.

395
00:26:20,030 --> 00:26:25,390
Actually, at first, I wanted him to be the lead actor. He will be the villain.

396
00:26:25,390 --> 00:26:28,100
Both of them would fight for you and both would get severely injured.

397
00:26:28,100 --> 00:26:29,780
But I thought it was too bloody.

398
00:26:29,780 --> 00:26:33,440
So I added romance to the story so that both of them

399
00:26:33,440 --> 00:26:35,140
would be madly in love with you.

400
00:26:35,140 --> 00:26:38,070
The problem lies in this part of them being "madly in love".

401
00:26:38,070 --> 00:26:39,240
What problem?

402
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:42,690
I can't even sense their love for the princess.

403
00:26:42,690 --> 00:26:47,400
So I don't understand the reasoning behind the princess's sacrifice.

404
00:26:49,010 --> 00:26:52,000
That's because they didn't get their lines right.

405
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:54,690
Zhang Qi, hurry up! Say the lines.

406
00:26:57,340 --> 00:27:01,260
She's my princess. I won't let you take her away.

407
00:27:01,260 --> 00:27:03,390
Done. It's your turn.

408
00:27:08,820 --> 00:27:11,871
That's impossible. The princess is my everything. Her voice makes me believe that all difficulties shall pass.

409
00:27:11,871 --> 00:27:13,550
The look in her eyes makes me believe that all good things will last forever.

410
00:27:13,550 --> 00:27:17,380
I'm at peace with the world. But if you want to take her away, I'm going to risk it all and fight you to the bitter end.

411
00:27:27,170 --> 00:27:31,790
Sunian, can you put some emotions into it?

412
00:27:31,790 --> 00:27:34,680
We're acting, not reading in the morning.

413
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:37,400
Even that has more emotions than you.

414
00:27:39,490 --> 00:27:40,860
Hurry. Practice!

415
00:27:40,860 --> 00:27:42,850
If you can't get it right, none of you can go home.

416
00:27:42,850 --> 00:27:45,940
Does that mean the dragon isn't needed anymore?

417
00:27:46,920 --> 00:27:48,920
Your part is easy. You may leave first.

418
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:50,820
Thank you, Director.

419
00:28:01,920 --> 00:28:05,060
<i>Zhang Qi, hurry! Again!</i>

420
00:28:05,060 --> 00:28:06,880
<i>I won't let you take her away.</i>

421
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:08,350
<i>She's my princess.</i>

422
00:28:08,350 --> 00:28:10,210
<i>I won't let you take her away.</i>

423
00:28:10,210 --> 00:28:12,350
<i>Five, six, seven, eight. Move.</i>

424
00:28:12,350 --> 00:28:16,830
<i>One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.</i>

425
00:28:16,830 --> 00:28:21,480
<i>Two, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.</i>

