00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:26,170
Three, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

427
00:28:26,170 --> 00:28:28,620
Two, two, three...

428
00:28:28,620 --> 00:28:30,340
- Shiyin, how are you?
