00:28:30,340 --> 00:28:33,150
- Are you all right?
- Let me take a look.

430
00:28:34,200 --> 00:28:37,350
I think she sprained her ankle. Take her to the infirmary.

431
00:28:41,480 --> 00:28:43,113
Why are you...

