00:29:23,473 --> 00:29:26,610
Are you okay? Does it hurt?

438
00:29:26,610 --> 00:29:30,160
I've heard what happened. That teacher is too much!

439
00:29:30,160 --> 00:29:33,530
Good thing Wu Huan was there. Wu Huan is awesome.

440
00:29:33,530 --> 00:29:35,580
Xue.

441
00:29:35,580 --> 00:29:36,680
What did the doctor say?

442
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:40,460
The doctor said it's nothing serious, but she won't be able to dance for a while.

443
00:29:46,330 --> 00:29:50,620
Shiyin, if you can't dance, so be it.

444
00:29:50,620 --> 00:29:53,650
It's not worth dancing for a teacher like that.

445
00:29:54,830 --> 00:29:57,800
I'm fine. I'll get going now.

446
00:30:01,040 --> 00:30:03,300
Walk with her.

447
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:16,300
Shao Xue.

448
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:19,350
What do you want this time?

449
00:30:19,350 --> 00:30:22,970
I still want to invite you to join the Drama Club and be a part of "Juliet."

450
00:30:22,970 --> 00:30:24,750
I have my own show.

451
00:30:24,750 --> 00:30:26,550
Are you sure you want to do this with them?

452
00:30:26,550 --> 00:30:30,550
I think a good actress like you needs a better partner.

453
00:30:30,550 --> 00:30:32,591
They don't deserve you.

454
00:30:32,591 --> 00:30:34,920
Wang Haoran, don't talk bad about my friends.

455
00:30:34,920 --> 00:30:37,220
I'll take on anyone who does that.

456
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:39,100
They don't even know how to act.

457
00:30:39,100 --> 00:30:41,640
Who are you talking about?

458
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:47,750
I'm only asking her to join the Drama Club.

459
00:30:47,750 --> 00:30:50,200
Why would she want to join your lousy club?

460
00:30:52,160 --> 00:30:55,550
- Are you sure you won't give it another thought?
- No.

461
00:30:56,790 --> 00:30:58,540
All right then.

462
00:30:58,540 --> 00:31:01,680
I wish you all the best.

463
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:05,313
Let's go.

464
00:31:06,160 --> 00:31:08,540
How did your rehearsal go?

465
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:11,393
- Not bad.
- Perfect.

466
00:31:11,393 --> 00:31:13,820
Don't screw up. Don't lose to that Romeo guy.

467
00:31:13,820 --> 00:31:16,590
- Don't worry.
- Come on. Let's go home.

468
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:24,400
We're off the clock. Let's go.

469
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:30,400
What's wrong?

470
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:33,200
The performance is tomorrow.

471
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:34,800
I'm a little nervous.

472
00:31:34,800 --> 00:31:38,100
But you did great when we were rehearsing.

473
00:31:38,100 --> 00:31:42,600
But once I get on the stage, I'll start having stage fright.

474
00:31:42,600 --> 00:31:45,600
I dare not face the audience,

475
00:31:45,600 --> 00:31:48,000
