476
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:50,000
The audience?

477
00:31:52,310 --> 00:31:53,590
How about this?

478
00:31:53,600 --> 00:31:56,800
Don't treat the audience as people.

479
00:31:57,700 --> 00:31:59,400
That's not what I meant.

480
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:01,900
I'm saying...

481
00:32:05,900 --> 00:32:08,600
You can treat the audience as boxes.

482
00:32:08,600 --> 00:32:11,200
This warehouse is the stage.

483
00:32:12,600 --> 00:32:14,000
This is Xue.

484
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:15,400
This is Sunian.

485
00:32:15,400 --> 00:32:17,800
This is Zhang Qi.

486
00:32:17,800 --> 00:32:19,000
Also...

487
00:32:19,800 --> 00:32:21,000
This.

488
00:32:23,600 --> 00:32:25,200
This is me.

489
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:28,600
Give it a try in front of them.

490
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:33,400
